to talk to me about the truth?

36:17.909 --> 36:21.813
You and Mom always arguing
and fighting about finding Andy,

36:21.847 --> 36:23.882
but pretending
everything is okay?

36:23.915 --> 36:26.352
Do you think
about what that means?

36:26.385 --> 36:28.420
Don't you want him to come back?

36:28.454 --> 36:30.322
Of course I do.

36:30.356 --> 36:32.324
But, Dad,

36:32.358 --> 36:36.428
back in Atlanta,
we killed 15 people.

36:36.462 --> 36:39.531
I've been looking them up.
I know their names.

36:39.565 --> 36:41.166
I know their kids' names.

36:41.199 --> 36:43.369
But you and Mom have never once
talked about that day.

36:43.402 --> 36:45.871
Or what it might mean for me
to have Andy come home.

36:45.904 --> 36:47.573
I had no idea. I'm sorry.

36:47.606 --> 36:48.640
So am I.

36:51.543 --> 36:53.545
Every day.

36:59.485 --> 37:00.886
